  "detailed_description": "Not The Name We Wanted is a parody.<br><br>It is definitely, positively and legally, NOT that carjacking game that seemed to do so well.<br><br>This top-selling short tour of the glories of the UK’s M4 corridor is easy to play, hard to master, addictive, very funny, and stupidly cheap.<br><br>100% of the profits from this game go to young people’s charity Peer Productions. Without Peer Productions the NotGames team would never have met. By buying this game you can help us pay something back.<br><br>NotGames: Sticking it to the virtual man since about ten minutes ago.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/369580/extras/b086eeafe3b07ac2accf989af0b35409.webp?t=1666029394\" width=40 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/369580/extras/abb8a682ce93cae71b1d026972596991.webp?t=1666029394\" width=40 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/369580/extras/d979092c9aaadf32134247d0d03e406c.webp?t=1666029394\" width=40 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/369580/extras/8ca5668cb1f2ffa632078ab772c79e3d.webp?t=1666029394\" width=40 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/369580/extras/6b9570f6ae4e802e5a3cabd38d968c77.webp?t=1666029394\" width=40 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/369580/extras/0ed66b36303c246d602fa1122ea74367.webp?t=1666029394\" width=40 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c